---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Documentation - Moaiy" description="Moaiy documentation for installation, source build, and security reporting.">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-bg-primary py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">
          Documentation
        </h1>
        <p class="font-body text-xl text-text-secondary">
          Practical docs for the current Moaiy macOS application
        </p>
      </div>

      <section class="mb-12 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">Quick Start</h2>
        <ol class="font-body text-text-secondary space-y-5">
          <li>
            <span class="text-accent-primary font-semibold">1. Download</span>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Get the latest DMG from
              <a
                href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/releases"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-accent-primary hover:underline"
              >
                GitHub Releases
              </a>.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="text-accent-primary font-semibold">2. Open the app</span>
            <p class="mt-2">Install the DMG package and launch Moaiy on macOS.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="text-accent-primary font-semibold">3. Create or import keys</span>
            <p class="mt-2">Use the app UI to generate/import OpenPGP keys, then encrypt/decrypt text or files.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">Build From Source</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-4">
          If you prefer local builds, use the official repository:
        </p>
        <div class="bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg p-5 font-code text-sm text-text-secondary overflow-x-auto">
          <div>git clone https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy.git</div>
          <div>cd moaiy</div>
          <div>open Moaiy/Moaiy.xcodeproj</div>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mt-4 mb-3">Or build/test via CLI:</p>
        <div class="bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg p-5 font-code text-sm text-text-secondary overflow-x-auto">
          <div>xcodebuild -project Moaiy/Moaiy.xcodeproj -scheme Moaiy -destination 'platform=macOS' build</div>
          <div class="mt-2">xcodebuild test -project Moaiy/Moaiy.xcodeproj -scheme Moaiy -destination 'platform=macOS'</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">Core Docs</h2>
        <ul class="font-body text-text-secondary space-y-3">
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/blob/main/README.md"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-accent-primary hover:underline"
            >
              README
            </a>
            <span> - product overview and setup.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-accent-primary hover:underline"
            >
              CONTRIBUTING
            </a>
            <span> - contribution workflow and testing expectations.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/tree/main/doc"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-accent-primary hover:underline"
            >
              doc/
            </a>
            <span> - architecture and technical notes.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/blob/main/SECURITY.md"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-accent-primary hover:underline"
            >
              SECURITY
            </a>
            <span> - private vulnerability reporting process.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">Release Verification</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Each release includes checksum information in release notes. Verify downloaded assets before
          first run when distributing in sensitive environments.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-bg-secondary to-bg-tertiary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">Need Help?</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <a
            href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/issues"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="bg-bg-primary rounded-lg p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-accent-primary/50 transition-all"
          >
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">GitHub Issues</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-text-secondary text-sm">Report bugs and request features.</p>
          </a>
          <a
            href="mailto:support@moaiy.com"
            class="bg-bg-primary rounded-lg p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-accent-primary/50 transition-all"
          >
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Support Email</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-text-secondary text-sm">support@moaiy.com</p>
          </a>
          <a
            href="mailto:security@moaiy.com"
            class="bg-bg-primary rounded-lg p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-accent-primary/50 transition-all"
          >
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Security Report</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-text-secondary text-sm">Use private disclosure only.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
